title: SprinSole Omni Custom Insoles
description: SprinSole are AFFORDABLE 100% custom insoles for your feet and provide all-day pain relief arch support in your beloved shoes, with double layer extra arch support. W/O leaving home, users just need to scan your feet with iPhone depth sensor or Android photogrammetry. With 3D data, we use an AI foot generative model to automate design and 3D printing personalized insoles with minimum manual involvement. Thus, we slash the cost well below $70 due to efficiency of our AI driven operation model.
